23
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:25,519
V, Leo Tolstoy, or C, William Shakespeare?

24
00:01:25,519 --> 00:01:28,560
I think I'm going to get it right today, Alice.

25
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:31,359
I'm going to say A, Miguel de Cervantes.

26
00:01:31,359 --> 00:01:36,159
Hmm, well, we'll find out later on in the show if you're right or not.

27
00:01:36,159 --> 00:01:39,119
But first, do you think shivalry is dead, Neil?

28
00:01:39,119 --> 00:01:42,719
No, not at all. These traditions are alive and kicking.

29
